{"tid":1725134,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"其實跳返出個圈諗下啦","createTime":"2019-11-15T16:02:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T16:27:39.000Z","uid":280214,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"33cdb35184b1ce9735f81630c9e4903f241537ba","tid":1725134,"uid":280214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:02:40.000Z","msg":"依家我地要既係Keep住閒日三罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係味先<br />\n<br />\n咁塞吐露港ok <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />紅隧ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />獅隧ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但話沒話除左三條隧道以外唔塞得WOR<br />\n<br />\n依家好多人既視線都轉左做守U，U守唔撚到就GG(普遍見到）然後就一堆人跳出尼話坳話U要人定唔要人。<br />\n<br />\n然後剩低既選擇就會變左<br />\n入U<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同撤U<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後第二日就會又有po話邊間要人邊間要人之後最撚精銳果班入撚曬去，之後再loop多次上面咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後班狗放架狗車係條路到，彈出彈入，上曬盾推一推之後又縮一縮，之後撚到我地出汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後其他區既手足就愈尼愈少。（範圍性愈尼愈細）<br />\n<br />\n首先我地要諗組織清楚三罷既行動主要集中係（範圍性同成效性方面）<br />\n<br />\n堵路(範圍性高，成效性高）<br />\n守U（範圍性低，成效性高）<br />\n<br />\n唔係話叫大家唔好守CU Poly  BU 但唔該針對返三罷既行動要有個平衡點平衡返範圍性同成效性。<br />\n<br />\n最好兼顧到，夠人守U又夠人 keep住遍地開花咁<br />\n<br />\n兩極化只會導致效率下降比人，唔好比U既人撤曬同時都都唔好叫曬出面既手足入曬。"},{"pid":"3bf175c887566047265f95ce84ecd02619699707","tid":1725134,"uid":280214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:04:30.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"7af22cfa053a16bccfa8dd6353cf3b076069f33d","tid":1725134,"uid":280214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:05:59.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"bac94324e928a52efb1fafd0a173f27d8777b289","tid":1725134,"uid":280214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:06:46.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"3bfbfd97fdc9615ba012ab25b09104820f6c844a","tid":1725134,"uid":280214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:07:18.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"f47f536117bb15b3657dd1683763a3be715eaa1b","tid":1725134,"uid":280214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:08:40.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"15726063a7de5c7e72b754269bf98877f6d0ba22","tid":1725134,"uid":280214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:11:05.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"505a6ce97c7da8c597da949ac0920cc62697b3a3","tid":1725134,"uid":280214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:12:15.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"504d9db50ccb5fb038b792f54421546643bafb28","tid":1725134,"uid":280214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:15:14.000Z","msg":"posh"},{"pid":"01390aa36c9a6488f8f7444b5683b935306e8e97","tid":1725134,"uid":280214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:17:44.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"8e460dc636fe5e93ab3679891e1ec68e49400f36","tid":1725134,"uid":280214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:27:39.000Z","msg":"pish"}]}